浪漫和爱情
Romance and love

500
00:41:54,870 --> 00:41:58,163
太过神秘 对此他早已缴械投降
was a mysterious language he'd given up on.

501
00:41:58,873 --> 00:42:02,082
要是玛丽只是问他烤箱的工作原理
lf only Mary had asked how a toaster works

